<form class="formDirectDebit">
    <style>
      .txt-color {
        color: #3f6cfd;
      }

      .text-height {
        line-height: 1.3;
      }

      .formDirectDebit h6 {
        font-size: 17px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .formDirectDebit h3 {
        font-weight: 600;
      }
    </style>
    <div style="width: 900px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; background-color: #fff; padding: 20px 50px 20px 50px">
      <header class="text-center">
        <img width="350" src="../../web-images/CashD-flogo.png" alt="logo">
        <h3 class="text-center mt-4 txt-color">Direct Debit Request</h3>
      </header>
      <main class="mt-4">
        <div>
          <h6 class="text-right">DE User ID: 342189 / 483449</h6>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <div class="form-group row">
              <label class="pt-0 col-sm-3 col-form-label text-right">Company / Customer <br />Name
                (“Customer”)</label>
              <div class="col-sm-9">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="companyName" value="<%= directDebitForm?.company_name ? directDebitForm?.company_name : '' %>" placeholder="">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
              <label class="col-sm-3 col-form-label text-right">ACN / ABN</label>
              <div class="col-sm-9">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="acn" value="<%= directDebitForm?.acn_or_abn ? directDebitForm?.acn_or_abn : '' %>" placeholder="">
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-justify text-height">The Customer authorizes and requests CashD Trading Pty Ltd ABN (17 650
              146 731) trading as CashD (“CashD”)
              to until further notice in writing, debit or charge through the Bulk Electronic Clearing System (BECS) the
              account indicated below, in accordance with the Direct Debit Request Service Agreement provided.</p>

            <h6 class="txt-color">Name and address of financial institution at which account is held</h6>
            <div class="form-group row mt-4">
              <label class="col-sm-3 col-form-label text-right">Bank</label>
              <div class="col-sm-9">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="bank" value="<%= directDebitForm?.bank ? directDebitForm?.bank : '' %>" placeholder="">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
              <label class="col-sm-3 col-form-label text-right">Address</label>
              <div class="col-sm-9">
                <textarea type="text" class="form-control" name="address" rows="2" placeholder=""><%= directDebitForm?.address ? directDebitForm?.address : '' %></textarea>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
              <label class="col-sm-3 col-form-label text-right">City</label>
              <div class="col-sm-3">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="city" value="<%= directDebitForm?.city ? directDebitForm?.city : '' %>" placeholder="">
              </div>
              <label class="col-sm-1 col-form-label text-right">State</label>
              <div class="col-sm-2">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="state" value="<%= directDebitForm?.state ? directDebitForm?.state : '' %>" placeholder="">
              </div>
              <label class="col-sm-1 col-form-label text-right pl-0 pr-0">Postcode</label>
              <div class="col-sm-2">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="postcode" value="<%= directDebitForm?.postcode ? directDebitForm?.postcode : '' %>"  placeholder="">
              </div>
            </div>

            <h6 class="txt-color pt-3">Details of bank account to be debited</h6>
            <div class="form-group row mt-4">
              <label class="col-sm-3 col-form-label text-right">Name on Account</label>
              <div class="col-sm-9">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="nameOnAccount" value="<%= directDebitForm?.bank_account_name ? directDebitForm?.bank_account_name : '' %>" placeholder="">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
              <label class="col-sm-3 col-form-label text-right">BSB</label>
              <div class="col-sm-3">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="bsb" maxlength="7" minlength="6" value="<%= directDebitForm?.bsb ? directDebitForm?.bsb : '' %>" placeholder="">
              </div>
              <label class="col-sm-3 col-form-label text-right">Account Number</label>
              <div class="col-sm-3">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="accountNumber" maxlength="9" minlength="9" value="<%= directDebitForm?.account_number ? directDebitForm?.account_number : '' %>"  placeholder="">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group mb-4">
              <label class="text-primary">Bank Name</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control" name="bankName" value="<%= directDebitForm?.bank_name ? directDebitForm.bank_name : '' %>" placeholder="Bank Name">
            </div>
            <h6 class="txt-color pt-3">Acknowledgement</h6>
            <p class="text-justify text-height">By signing this Direct Debit Request and/or by providing a valid
              instruction with respect to the Customer’s
              Direct Debit Request, the Customer acknowledges that the Customer has read and understood the governing
              terms
              and conditions detailed in this Direct Debit Request and the Direct Debit Request Service Agreement and
              agrees
              to the debit arrangement between CashD and the Customer. The Customer further acknowledges that CashD will
              appear as the merchant on the Customer’s bank statement.</p>
            <p class="text-justify text-height">If this Direct Debit Request Form is signed by a person (including by a
              person on behalf of, or as an
              officer of, a person) by use of an electronic signature
              (including by signing on an electronic device or by digital signature, whether directly on the electronic
              document or by a platform for hosting electronic copies of documents), then the person unconditionally:
            </p>
            <p class="text-justify text-height">
              a) authorizes their use of an electronic signature be affixed or otherwise applied to this document
              (including
              to any digital copy of it);
            </p>
            <p class="text-justify text-height">
              b) agrees that, CashD Trading Pty Ltd (ACN 650 146 731 ) (”CashD”) and all other
              persons signing (at any time) any part of this Direct Debit Request (including any digital copy of it) may
              rely on the electronic signature as having the same force and effect as a handwritten signature on a paper
              copy of the Direct Debit Request and as though all persons signing this Direct Debit Request signed at the
              same time and in the same place in the presence of each other;
            </p>
            <p class="text-justify text-height">
              c) consents to any method the other persons use
              (at their discretion) to sign this Direct Debit Request (including to any digital copy of it), to any
              order of
              signing it and at the time of signing it without being in the presence of any other signatory;
            </p>
            <p class="text-justify text-height">
              d) confirms their intention to enter into a binding legal agreement however they and other persons sign
              this
              Direct Debit
              Request; and
            </p>
            <p class="text-justify text-height">
              e) to CashD using any method to identify any signatory and to verify the application by the
              signatory of that person’s electronic signature (but without any express or implied obligation to verify
              beyond reasonable doubt as to the application of the electronic signature).
            </p>

            <h6 class="text-right txt-color mb-3">CashD Trading Pty Ltd t/a CashD: ABN:17 650 146 731</h6>
